Class CatalogQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.catalog.querys.DiscoveryServiceQuery
      • org.gvsig.catalog.querys.CatalogQuery

  • public class CatalogQuery
extends DiscoveryServiceQuery
    This class implements a general query. It contains an attribute for each parameter that can be showed in the search form.
